  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is being conducted to evaluate the safety and tolerability of crofelemer 125 mg
      twice a day, taken orally, over 48 weeks of therapy in human immunodeficiency virus-positive
      (HIV+) subjects with diarrhea.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
